---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import NMJDifference from "../components/home/NMJDifference.astro";
import CallToAction from "../components/home/CallToAction.astro";
---

<MainLayout
	title="About"
	description="Learn about NMJ Electric, its owner, experience, and commitment to quality workmanship, fair pricing, and responsive service."
>
	<section class="about-hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">About NMJ Electric</p>
		<h1>Experienced Electrical Work Without the Corporate Overhead</h1>
		<p class="intro">
			NMJ Electric is a locally owned electrical contractor serving residential
			and commercial customers throughout the Dallas–Fort Worth area.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="story">
		<h2>Meet the Owner</h2>

		<p>
			NMJ Electric was founded by Mario Gonzales, a licensed Texas Master
			Electrician with experience in electrical construction, troubleshooting,
			maintenance, commercial facilities, fire alarm systems, and project
			management.
		</p>

		<p>
			Before entering the electrical trade, Mario served as a Sergeant in the
			United States Marine Corps. That background helped shape the company’s
			approach: communicate clearly, take responsibility, and complete the work
			correctly.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="purpose">
		<h2>Why NMJ Electric Was Started</h2>

		<p>
			NMJ Electric was created to provide customers with professional electrical
			service without unnecessary markups, rushed workmanship, or poor
			communication.
		</p>

		<p>
			The goal is simple: offer competitive pricing, take the time to perform
			quality work, and respond quickly throughout the entire project.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="credentials">
		<h2>Experience and Credentials</h2>

		<ul>
			<li>Licensed Texas Master Electrician</li>
			<li>Residential and commercial electrical experience</li>
			<li>Electrical troubleshooting and maintenance</li>
			<li>Facilities and project management experience</li>
			<li>United States Marine Corps veteran</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<NMJDifference />
	<CallToAction />
</MainLayout>

<style>
	.about-hero,
	.story,
	.purpose,
	.credentials {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 0;
	}

	.about-hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 1rem;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		color: #0f3d73;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #4b5563;
	}

	.story p,
	.purpose p,
	.credentials li {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #374151;
	}

	.credentials ul {
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
	}

	.credentials li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}
</style>